      <div xml:id="NA137-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu talaivaṉ celavu aḻuṅkiyatu. (ETv: celaviṭai aḻuṅkal collāmai aṉṟē, vaṉpuṟai kuṟitta tavircciyāta...(?))</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how they prevents HIM from going.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA137">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            taṇṇiya kamaḻun tāḻiruṅ kūntaṟ</l>
<l>            ṟaṭameṉ paṇaittōṇ maṭanal lāḷvayiṟ</l>
<l>            piriyac cūḻntaṉai yāyi ṉariyatoṉ</l>
<l>            ṟeytiṉai vāḻiya neñcē cevvarai</l>
<l>            yaruvi yāṉṟa nīri ṉīḷiṭaik </l>
<l>            kayantalai maṭappiṭi yuyaṅkupaci kaḷaiiyar</l>
<l>            peruṅkaḷiṟu tolaitta muṭattā ḷōmai</l>
<l>            yaruñcurañ celvōrk kalkuniḻa lākuṅ</l>
<l>            kuṉṟa vaippiṉ kāṉañ</l>
<l>            ceṉṟucē ṇakaṟal valliya nīyē.</l>
            </lg>
       <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent3">If you have considered separating</l>
<l rend="indent4">from the good one with broad soft bamboo shoulders</l>
<l rend="indent4">[and] hanging dark tresses that smell coolly,</l>
<l>you have achieved something difficult, may you live, heart,</l>
<l>– you who have the strength to leave for the distance, going</l>
<l rend="indent3">through the forest of the hill region,</l>
<l rend="indent">where the crooked Ōmai tree, destroyed by the big elephant bull</l>
<l rend="indent2">to remove the hunger weakening the soft-headed youthful	elephant cow,</l>
<l rend="indent3">on the waterless long way left by the waterfalls from the red mountain,</l>
<l>becomes shade to abide in for those going through the difficult desert.</l>
<lg type="alternate" sameAs="3+4b">
    <l>In case you considered separating ...,</l>
 	<l>you would plan something difficult...</l>

</lg>
        </lg>
